{"tid":383144,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求評］鹿兒島、宮崎、指宿自駕行程","createTime":"2017-09-01T09:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T09:48:01.000Z","uid":71647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd520a4433e2f58949c0b4ac8c060e6378ff13ea","tid":383144,"uid":71647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"同老母去六日 自駕<br />\n暫時諗住<br />\nDay1 三點幾落機 拎車去宮崎食晚飯 宿宮崎<br />\nDay2 去鬼之洗衫板、日南復活島像 食宮崎牛加海鮮 宿宮崎<br />\nDay3 一早去霧島神宮、大浪池 中午後到櫻島 再搭船然後揸去指宿 宿指宿<br />\nDay4 浸溫泉 砂浴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下午返鹿兒島 宿鹿兒島<br />\nDay5 鹿兒島市內 宿鹿兒島<br />\nDay6 shopping 加走人<br />\n<br />\n我覺得day3好似好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a72bf48faf07ba13814e3a951254230d556006","tid":383144,"uid":21259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"我係頭尾嗰日都住鹿兒島 我由下面玩返上去"},{"pid":"3d34784fb175c2dc8a5ea495843936798841abb2","tid":383144,"uid":71647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係頭尾嗰日都住鹿兒島 我由下面玩返上去</blockquote><br />\n分別住指宿 霧島 宮崎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56eb81412834ceb858d0548c6b0a2dc484e0e6e1","tid":383144,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"第三日車程太長 一係cut走櫻島一係cut走指宿放落第四日<br />\n如果唔係全日連走馬看花都談唔上"},{"pid":"de64493cf9da4977ede6081f1dca890d50d2212e","tid":383144,"uid":121562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"day2早少少起身去完公園去埋霧島神宮夜晚唔返宮崎就住霧島<br />\nday3繼續原本行程<br />\n我試過霧島出發，去飫肥城-鵜戶神宮-日南公園-青島神宮剛好一日"},{"pid":"cca34c9c083b12f3b30bb74aa3b259f0149838f6","tid":383144,"uid":71647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>day2早少少起身去完公園去埋霧島神宮夜晚唔返宮崎就住霧島<br />\nday3繼續原本行程<br />\n我試過霧島出發，去飫肥城-鵜戶神宮-日南公園-青島神宮剛好一日</blockquote><br />\n好似幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858121550308a20f9b1adbc749c4417a6a965f26","tid":383144,"uid":71647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第三日車程太長 一係cut走櫻島一係cut走指宿放落第四日<br />\n如果唔係全日連走馬看花都談唔上</blockquote><br />\n就係覺得太長 由頭揸到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}